{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012",
		"name": "POC Microservices - CQRS/SAGA/Event Sourcing",
		"description": "API collection for Spring Cloud microservices with CQRS, SAGA, and Event Sourcing patterns\n\n## Write Flow (Event Sourcing)\n1. **Create Product** → `CreateProductCommand` → `ProductAggregate.applyProductCreated()` → `EventStore.save()` → `DomainEventPublisher` → Kafka `[product-events]`\n2. **Update Product** → `UpdateProductCommand` → `ProductAggregate.updateName/Price/...` → `applyProductUpdated(old,new)` → `EventStore.saveAll()` → `DomainEventPublisher` → Kafka `[product-events]`\n\n## Variables\n- `product_id`: set automatically by Create Product test script\n- `updated_name`: set automatically by Update Product test scripts\n- `updated_price`: set automatically by Update Product test scripts",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
